Currently, [section 9.b](http://www.adobe.com/devnet/opentype/afdko/topic_feature_file_syntax.html#9.b) of the OpenType Feature File specification does not make it clear whether the same glyph can have both LigatureCaretByPos and LigatureCaretByIndex statements. Should this be allowed? Might be good to clarify the spec.

Example:
```
table GDEF {
     LigatureCaretByPos [c_t c_s]  500;
     LigatureCaretByIndex c_t 5;
} GDEF;
```

